Name: Ancient Astra
Desc:
[Enchant Force]
Materializes an arrow of the legends to bombard enemies with a powerful attack.
Discharge Enhancement
Additional magic arrows are created from hit enemies.
Blast Enhancement
Aims and shoots a significantly powerful arrow at the enemy.
Transition Enhancement
Enables movement while attacking.

H.Old:
Relic Gauge Cost: 65 per sec. Hold the Skill key to attack up to 7 enemies at 320% damage 6 times.
Cooldown: 60 sec.
